    <div class="gk-tip">
      <strong>Current count: 14 notified major ports</strong> (12 operational + Vadhavan under construction + Galathea Bay under construction). The long-standing "12 major ports" figure is now outdated. Legal basis: <strong>Major Port Authorities Act, 2021</strong> (replaced the Major Port Trusts Act, 1963). Total cargo by all major ports in FY 2024-25: <strong>~855 million tonnes</strong> (4.3% growth, record).
    </div>

