              <td><strong>JNPT</strong><br><small>(Jawaharlal Nehru Port / Nhava Sheva)</small></td>
              <td>Maharashtra</td>
              <td>1989</td>
              <td>Commissioned 1989. <strong>India's largest container port</strong> — handled 7.3 million TEUs in FY 2024-25 (record, 13.5% YoY growth). Located south of Mumbai across Thane Creek.</td>
