              <td>4</td>
              <td><strong>Mormugao Port</strong></td>
              <td>Goa</td>
              <td>1964</td>
              <td>Natural harbour. Current site operational since 1885. Declared major port 1964. Known for iron ore exports from Goa's mining belt.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>5</td>
              <td><strong>New Mangalore Port</strong></td>
              <td>Karnataka</td>
