              <td><strong>Natural harbour</strong> — formed naturally in 1341 AD when the Periyar River flooded. Brought under Major Port Trusts Act on 1 August 1936. <strong>Nearest major port to the Suez Canal route</strong> (~76 nautical miles from Suez route). Houses ICTT Vallarpadam, India's largest container transshipment terminal.</td>
            </tr>
